headline: Moody’s Corporation to Present at the J.P. Morgan Ultimate Services Conference on November 14, 2024
summary: NEW YORK, November 07, 2024--Moody’s Corporation (NYSE: MCO) announced today that Noémie Heuland, Chief Financial Officer, will speak at the J.P. Morgan Ultimate Services Conference on Thursday, November 14, 2024. The presentation will begin at approximately 1:50 p.m. Eastern Time and the audio will be webcast live. The audio webcast will be accessible at Moody’s Investor Relations website, ir.moodys.com.
